"enable": "boolean", Enable auto-capacityThe object must be set\nbefore any other auto capacity configuration\nis supplied for the tunnel,and must be the\nlast auto-capacity configuration object to be\nremoved.

    
"clones-maximum": "integer", Upper limit on the number of clones can be\ncreated for the tunnel
range: "0..63"
default: "63"
 
    
"split-bandwidth": "integer", Upper bandwidth limit that causes the tunnel\nto be split
range: "0..4294967295"
units: "kbit/s"
 
    
"clones-minimum": "integer", Lower limit on the number of clones can be\ncreated for the tunnel
range: "0..63"
default: "0"
 
    
"merge-bandwidth": "integer" Lower bandwidth limit that causes the tunnel\nto be merged
range: "0..4294967295"
units: "kbit/s"
 
  }
}
